properties.sfomuseum:description: Handwritten letter from Harold M. Bixby to his wife, Debby Bixby, undated, on Radiogram from from the Chinese Government Radio Administration; includes description of the reception of Mr. Bixby’s book on “mail movements in China” by Mr. Dai [Enki], with a list of Chinese officials who received a copy; mentions Chinese officials T.V. Soong, M.Y. Tang, Lin Sen, Sun Fo, Wang Ching Wei, Chiang Kai-shek, Ho Ying Ching.
